truffle-ts is a browser-native reimplementation of the EC2 instance-discovery
model of the spore.host `truffle` tool (https://github.com/spore-host/truffle).

The bundled instance catalog (src/data/instances.json) and static pricing
(src/data/pricing.ts) are approximate snapshots ("as of 2026-01"), not live
AWS data.
